<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE reference PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Reference//EN" "reference.dtd">
<reference id="api_startscreencapture">
    <title><ph keyref="startScreenCapture"/></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc"><?oxy-placeholder content="Provide a short description for this API."?>Starts screen sharing.</ph></shortdesc>
    <prolog>
        <metadata>
            <keywords>
                <indexterm keyref="startScreenCapture"/>
            </keywords>
        </metadata>
    </prolog>
    <refbody>
        <section id="prototype">
            <p outputclass="codeblock">
                <codeblock props="android" outputclass="language-java">public abstract int startScreenCapture( Intent mediaProjectionPermissionResultData, ScreenCaptureParameters parameters);</codeblock>
                <codeblock props="ios mac" outputclass="language-objectivec"/>
                <codeblock props="windows" outputclass="language-cpp">virtual int startScreenCapture(void* mediaProjectionPermissionResultData, const ScreenCaptureParameters&amp; captureParams) = 0;</codeblock>
                <codeblock props="electron" outputclass="language-typescript"/>
                <codeblock props="unity" outputclass="language-csharp"/>
                <codeblock props="rn" outputclass="language-typescript"/>
                <codeblock props="flutter" outputclass="language-dart"/>
            </p>
        </section>
        <section id="detailed_desc">
            <p>成功调用该方法后，你可以通过 Android 系统原生的 <xref keyref="MediaProjection-link">MediaProjectionLink</xref> 对整个屏幕进行共享。<note type="attention">
                <ul>
                    <li>This method is for Android and iOS only.</li>
                    <li>Call this method after joining a channel.</li>
                    <li>调用该方法前，你需要通过业务逻辑获取 Android 原生 <xref keyref="onActivityResult-link">onActivityResult</xref> 回调的 <parmname>data</parmname> 参数。</li>
                    <li>在 Android 10 或之后版本上屏幕共享时，为避免 Android 系统触发 <xref keyref="SecurityException-link">SecurityException</xref>，请在调用 <apiname keyref="MediaProjection-link"/> 前先调用 Android 原生的 <xref keyref="startForeground-link">startForeground</xref>，通知用户当前设备正在屏幕共享。</li>
                    </ul>
                </note></p>
        </section>
        <section id="parameters"><title>Parameter</title>
            <parml>
                <plentry>
                    <pt><b>mediaProjectionPermissionResultData</b></pt>
                    <pd>
                        <p>传入 <apiname>onActivity</apiname> 回调的 <parmname>data</parmname> 参数。</p>
                    </pd>
                </plentry>
                <plentry>
                    <pt><b>captureParams</b></pt>
                    <pd>
                        <p>The screen sharing encoding parameters. The default video dimension is 1920 x 1080, that is, 2,073,600 pixels. Agora uses the value of this parameter to calculate the charges. For details, see <xref keyref="ScreenCaptureParameters"/>.</p>
                    </pd>
                </plentry>
            </parml>
        </section>
        <section id="return_values">
            <title>Returns</title>
            <ul>
                <li>0: Success.</li>
                <li>&lt; 0: Failure.<ul>
                        <li>-2(<codeph>ERR_INVALID_ARGUMENT</codeph>): <parmname>mediaProjectionPermissionResultData</parmname> 参数为空。</li>
                    </ul></li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </refbody>
</reference>
